Description: Provides a targets Target Factory (Archetype) that offloads heavy
    targets to Azure ML Compute Clusters as asynchronous Command Jobs. Job state
    is tracked via JSON token files on a shared Azure Blob storage mount so that
    pipelines survive local computer sleep and reboot cycles.
